Game Architecture - Spring 2012


Homework 2 - Vector & Matrix, Cube Transformation
    Compiling:
        To build:
           $ cmake .
           $ make
           Ought to produce a hw2 binary in ./bin/ simply run that to get to the prompt. input is function name followed by any arguements separated by a space. help lists all available functions.

Homework 3 - Quaternions / SQT
    Compiling is the same as Homework 2, ought to produce hw3 binary in addition to the hw2 one in ./bin/ prompt is identical in function to that of hw2.